# Seravolve - Clinical Skincare Formulated for Indian Skin

## Brand Overview
Seravolve is a clinical skincare brand expertly formulated to target specific skin concerns, especially for Indian skin types. We focus on complete, synchronized routines rather than single ingredients, eliminating the guesswork from skincare.

## Core Philosophy
We believe in systems that work. Our synchronized routines are designed specifically for:
- Acne & Blemishes
- Dryness & Dehydration
- Dullness & Pigmentation
- Enlarged Pores & Texture
- UV & Sun Damage

## Concern Protocols

### Acne Protocol
Designed to clear congestion and prevent future breakouts without compromising the skin barrier. 
Routine: Clarifying Face Wash (2% Salicylic Acid), Radiance Toner (3% Niacinamide), Barrier Repair Moisturizer.

### Dryness Protocol
Engineered to restore clarity and deep hydration.
Routine: Hydrating Cleanser, Barrier Repair Moisturizer (Ceramides & Hyaluronic Acid).

### Pigmentation Protocol
Engineered to restore clarity and visibly reduce dark spots and uneven tone.
Routine: Radiance Toner (Rice Water), Vitamin C Serum, Barrier Repair Moisturizer.

### Pores & Texture Protocol
Designed specifically to clear congestion and minimize pore visibility.
Routine: Clarifying Face Wash (2% Salicylic), Radiance Toner (3% Niacinamide).

### UV & Sun Damage Protocol
Advanced protection and repair.
Routine: Daily UV Defense Sunscreen (SPF 50), Barrier Repair Moisturizer.

## Ingredient & Efficacy Standards
- Cruelty-Free: Never tested on animals. All efficacy testing is conducted through in-vitro studies and voluntary human trials.
- Clean Formulations: Paraben-free, Sulfate-free, DEA-free. Non-comedogenic.
- Shelf Life: 12 months after opening (12M PAO).

